Package: moimix
Title: moimix: Estimating mulitplicity of infection from high-throughput sequencing data
Version: 0.0.0.0
Authors@R: "Stuart Lee <lee.s@wehi.edu.au> [aut, cre]"
Description: R package to evaluate multiplicity of infection (MOI) of organims using 
    binomial mixture models and other population genetics methods. moimix can be used to simulate 
    single nucleotide variant (SNV) data from samples with known MOI. 
Depends:
    flexmix
License: MIT + file LICENSE
LazyData: true
Imports:
    MCMCpack,
    foreach,
    SeqArray,
    SeqVarTools,
    Rcpp
Suggests:
    testthat,
    knitr,
    rmarkdown
VignetteBuilder: knitr
RoxygenNote: 5.0.1
LinkingTo: Rcpp
